#. </p><p>
msgctxt "sn56.56:0.2"
msgid "6. Abhisamayavagga"
msgstr "6. Comprehension"

#. </p><h1>
#. VAR: 56. Dutiyamahāpathavīsutta → dutiyapaṭhavisuttaṃ (bj) | paṭhavī 2 (pts1)
msgctxt "sn56.56:0.3"
msgid "56. Dutiyamahāpathavīsutta"
msgstr "56. The Earth (2nd)"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "sn56.56:1.1"
msgid ""
"“Seyyathāpi, bhikkhave, mahāpathavī parikkhayaṃ pariyādānaṃ gaccheyya "
"ṭhapetvā satta kolaṭṭhimattiyo guḷikā."
msgstr ""
"“Mendicants, suppose the great earth was worn away and eroded except for "
"seven clay balls the size of jujube seeds."

msgctxt "sn56.56:1.2"
msgid "Taṃ kiṃ maññatha, bhikkhave, "
msgstr "What do you think, mendicants? "

msgctxt "sn56.56:1.3"
msgid ""
"katamaṃ nu kho bahutaraṃ—yaṃ vā mahāpathaviyā parikkhīṇaṃ pariyādinnaṃ, yā "
"vā satta kolaṭṭhimattiyo guḷikā avasiṭṭhā”ti?"
msgstr ""
"Which is more: the great earth that has been worn away and eroded, or the "
"seven clay balls the size of jujube seeds that are left?”"

msgctxt "sn56.56:1.4"
msgid ""
"“Etadeva, bhante, bahutaraṃ mahāpathaviyā yadidaṃ parikkhīṇaṃ pariyādinnaṃ; "
"appamattikā satta kolaṭṭhimattiyo guḷikā avasiṭṭhā."
msgstr ""
"“Sir, the great earth that has been worn away and eroded is certainly more. "
"The seven clay balls the size of jujube seeds are tiny."

msgctxt "sn56.56:1.5"
msgid ""
"Saṅkhampi na upenti, upanidhampi na upenti, kalabhāgampi na upenti "
"mahāpathaviyā parikkhīṇaṃ pariyādinnaṃ upanidhāya satta kolaṭṭhimattiyo "
"guḷikā avasiṭṭhā”ti."
msgstr ""
"Compared to the great earth that has been worn away and eroded, they can’t "
"be reckoned or compared, they’re not even a fraction.”"

msgctxt "sn56.56:1.6"
msgid "“Evameva kho, bhikkhave, ariyasāvakassa … pe …"
msgstr "“In the same way, for a noble disciple …"

msgctxt "sn56.56:1.7"
msgid "yogo karaṇīyo”ti."
msgstr "That’s why you should practice meditation …”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn56.56:1.8"
msgid "Chaṭṭhaṃ."
msgstr ""
